SELECT /*+PARALLEL(#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_PARALLEL)*/ A.TMCODE||'-'||A.SPCODE COD_PLAN, A.TMCODE, A.SPCODE, CASE WHEN (A.SNCODE=3013) THEN (B.VLR_CFM) ELSE (A.ACCESSFEE) END VLR_CFM, A.ACCGLCODE, A.USGGLCODE, A.VSCODE, A.VSDATE FROM #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_SYSADM.MPULKTMB A LEFT JOIN ( SELECT /*+PARALLEL(#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_PARALLEL)*/ TMCODE, SPCODE, VSCODE, SUM(ACCESSFEE) VLR_CFM FROM #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_SYSADM.MPULKTMB WHERE SNCODE IN (3013,11538,11537) GROUP BY TMCODE, SPCODE, VSCODE ) B ON (A.TMCODE = B.TMCODE AND A.SPCODE = B.SPCODE AND A.VSCODE = B.VSCODE) WHERE A.SNCODE IN (3013,3)

SELECT /*+PARALLEL(#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_PARALLEL)*/ TMCODE, INITCAP(REPLACE(DES,CHR(10),'')) PLAN_DESC, VSDATE FROM #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_SYSADM.MPUTMTAB WHERE VSCODE = (SELECT MAX(VSCODE) FROM #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_SYSADM.MPUTMTAB TM WHERE MPUTMTAB.TMCODE = TM.TMCODE) AND STATUS='P'

SELECT /*+PARALLEL(#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_PARALLEL)*/ DISTINCT TMCODE||'-'||SPCODE AS COD_PLAN , DECODE(PREPAGO,0,'Prepago','Postpago') AS PRODUCTO , DECODE(PREPAGO,3,'DATOS','VOZ') AS GRP_SERVICIO , CASE WHEN PREPAGO IN (1,4,5) THEN '2' WHEN PREPAGO IN (2) THEN '1' WHEN PREPAGO IN (3) THEN '3' ELSE '9' END PLANTYPEID , CASE WHEN PREPAGO IN (1,4,5) THEN 'Cerrado' WHEN PREPAGO IN (2) THEN 'Abierto' WHEN PREPAGO IN (3) THEN 'Datos' ELSE 'Otro' END PLANTYPEID_DESC , PREPAGO AS TIPO_PLAN_MINACTIVO , MICROCELDA , CATE_PLAN AS CATE_PLAN_MINACTIVO , CASE WHEN UPPER(SUBSTR(CLASE_PLAN,INSTR(CLASE_PLAN,',',1,4)+1,(INSTR(CLASE_PLAN,',',1,5)-INSTR(CLASE_PLAN,',',1,4))-1))='PYMES' THEN 'S' ELSE 'N' END BAN_PYME FROM #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_SYSADM.INH_TMSP_PREP
SNP_PROJECT : CAPACITACION #SNP_FOLDER : DAVID #SNP_PACKAGE : ETL #SNP_SCEN : SC_JH_0772_CLIEN_CARGA_OBJETOS_NZLOAD Version 001

SELECT /*+PARALLEL(#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_PARALLEL)*/ TMCODE, CASE WHEN EQUIVALENCIA = 1 THEN 'S' ELSE NULL END BAN_REVENTA, CASE WHEN EQUIVALENCIA = 2 THEN DESARROLLO ELSE NULL END INDICADOR_PLAN, CASE WHEN EQUIVALENCIA = 1 THEN 'REVENTA' ELSE 'INDICADOR' END REVENTA_INDICADOR FROM sysadm.INH_CONFIG_PLANES WHERE EQUIVALENCIA IN (1,2)

SELECT /*+PARALLEL(#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_PARALLEL)*/ A.TMCODE, A.SPCODE, MAX(A.VERSION) AS VER FROM #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_SYSADM.INH_DETALLE_PLAN_PAQ A GROUP BY A.TMCODE, A.SPCODE
SNP_PROJECT : CAPACITACION #SNP_FOLDER : DAVID #SNP_PACKAGE : ETL #SNP_SCEN : SC_JH_0772_CLIEN_CARGA_OBJETOS_NZLOAD Version 001

SELECT /*+PARALLEL(#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_PARALLEL)*/ D.TMCODE, D.SPCODE, D.TIPO_BOLSA, D.TIPO_CONTROL_MAGUARE, D.TIPO_PLAN, D.TIPO_MEDIDA, REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(D.DESCRIPCION,CHR(10),''),CHR(8),''),CHR(9),'') AS PLAN_DESC_COMPLETA, D.VERSION, CASE WHEN UPPER(D.TIPO_PLAN) = 'VOZ' THEN NVL(D.CFM_VOZ,0) + NVL(D.CFM_DATOS,0) + NVL(D.CFM_DATOS_IMP,0) WHEN UPPER(D.TIPO_PLAN) = 'BUNDLE' THEN NVL(D.CFM_VOZ,0) ELSE 0 END AS VLR_CFM_VOZ, CASE WHEN UPPER(D.TIPO_PLAN) = 'DATOS' THEN NVL(D.CFM_VOZ,0) WHEN UPPER(D.TIPO_PLAN) = 'BUNDLE' THEN NVL(D.CFM_DATOS,0) ELSE 0 END AS VLR_CFM_DATOS, CASE WHEN UPPER(D.TIPO_PLAN) IN ('DATOS','BUNDLE') THEN NVL(D.CFM_DATOS_IMP,0) ELSE 0 END AS VLR_CFM_DATOS_IMP, D.MIN_INC_C_F_O AS MIN_INC_C_F_O, D.MIN_INC_CLARO AS MIN_INC_C, D.MIN_INC_FIJOS AS MIN_INC_F, D.MIN_INC_OTROS AS MIN_INC_O, D.MIN_INC_ELEG_TD AS CANT_MIN_INC_ELEG_TD, D.CANT_MO_INC AS CANT_SMS_CLARO_INC, CAST(D.CANT_INC_MB AS INTEGER) AS CANT_MB_INC_PLAN, CAST(D.CANT_INC_MB_BB AS INTEGER) AS CANT_MB_BB_INC_PLAN, D.SEGMENTO AS SEGMENTO_PLAN, REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(D.NAVEGACION,CHR(10),''),CHR(8),''),CHR(9),'') AS NAVEGACION_PLAN, D.VALOR_RIH_CLARO AS VLR_MIN_INC_CLARO, D.VALOR_RIH_FIJOS AS VLR_MIN_INC_FIJOS, D.VALOR_RIH_OTROS AS VLR_MIN_INC_OTROS, D.VALOR_ADIC_CLARO AS VLR_MIN_ADIC_CLARO, D.VALOR_ADIC_FIJOS AS VLR_MIN_ADIC_FIJOS, D.VALOR_ADIC_OTROS AS VLR_MIN_ADIC_OTROS, D.VALOR_ADIC_MO AS VLR_SMS_ADIC_CLARO, D.ELEG_FIJO AS CANT_ELEG_FIJO, D.ELEG_ONNET AS CANT_ELEG_ONNET, D.ELEG_OFFNET AS CANT_ELEG_OFFNET, D.ELEG_TD AS CANT_ELEG_TD, REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(D.NOMBRE_CUOTA_PCRF,CHR(10),''),CHR(8),''),CHR(9),'') AS NOMBRE_CUOTA_PCRF, REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(D.ENTITLEMENT_PCRF,CHR(10),''),CHR(8),''),CHR(9),'') AS TIPO_NAVEGACION_PCRF, REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(D.TIPO_PCRF,CHR(10),''),CHR(8),''),CHR(9),'') AS TIPO_PLAN_PCRF, D.ROUTING_CATEGORY AS ROUTING_CATEGORY_BCSC, D.TECNOLOGIA, D.FAMILIA_PLAN, D.CLASE_PLAN, D.MIN_INC_LDI_1, D.MIN_INC_LDI_2, D.MIN_INC_LDI_RM, ROUND(D.VALOR_ADIC_KB,3) AS VALOR_ADIC_KB, T.PLAN_ID AS COD_PASE FROM #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_SYSADM.INH_DETALLE_PLAN_PAQ D LEFT JOIN #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_SYSADM.INH_PLANES_IOT T ON D.TMCODE = T.TMCODE

SELECT /*+PARALLEL(#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_PARALLEL)*/ DISTINCT NVL(D.TMCODE,V.TMCODE) AS TMCODE , NVL(D.SPCODE,V.SPCODE) AS SPCODE , CASE WHEN (D.TMCODE||D.SPCODE IS NULL) THEN '0' ELSE D.VALOR_KB END AS VALOR_KB , CASE WHEN (D.TMCODE||D.SPCODE IS NULL) THEN '0' ELSE D.CUOTA END AS CUOTA , CASE WHEN (D.TMCODE||D.SPCODE IS NULL) THEN '-' ELSE D.UNIDAD_CUOTA END AS UNIDAD_CUOTA , NVL(TIPO_OFERTA,'Na') TIPO_OFERTA , CASE WHEN (V.TMCODE||V.SPCODE IS NULL) THEN 'N' ELSE V.BAN_CONVERTIBLE_LDI END AS BAN_CONVERTIBLE_LDI , CASE WHEN (V.TMCODE||V.SPCODE IS NULL) THEN '0' ELSE V.PSB_MINU_CONV_LDI END AS PSB_MINU_CONV_LDI , CASE WHEN (V.TMCODE||V.SPCODE IS NULL) THEN '0' ELSE V.PSB_VALOR_CONV_LDI END AS PSB_VALOR_CONV_LDI , CASE WHEN (V.TMCODE||V.SPCODE IS NULL) THEN '0' ELSE V.PSB_VALOR_CONV_PREFERE_LDI END AS PSB_VALOR_CONV_PREFERE_LDI , CASE WHEN (V.TMCODE||V.SPCODE IS NULL) THEN '0' ELSE V.PSB_MINU_CONV_ZONA_LDI END AS PSB_MINU_CONV_ZONA_LDI , CASE WHEN (V.TMCODE||V.SPCODE IS NULL) THEN '0' ELSE V.PSB_VALOR_CONV_ZONA_LDI END AS PSB_VALOR_CONV_ZONA_LDI , CASE WHEN (V.TMCODE||V.SPCODE IS NULL) THEN '0' ELSE V.PSB_MINU_CONV_PREFERE_LDI END AS PSB_MINU_CONV_PREFERE_LDI , CASE WHEN (D.TMCODE||D.SPCODE IS NULL) THEN '0' ELSE D.CUOTA3 END AS DES_CONSU_ADI_DATOS , CASE WHEN (D.TMCODE||D.SPCODE IS NULL) THEN '-' ELSE D.TIME_PERIOD END AS COD_PERIODO_TIEMPO FROM ( SELECT CAP.TMCODE , MP.SPCODE , CAP.SNCODE , MP.REC_VERSION , CAP.VALOR_KB , CAP.CUOTA , CAP.UNIDAD_CUOTA , CAP.CUOTA3 , CAP.TIME_PERIOD , DESARROLLO FROM ( SELECT A.TMCODE , B.SNCODE , A.VALOR_KB , CASE WHEN (B.CUOTA IS NOT NULL) THEN SUBSTR(B.CUOTA,0,LENGTH(B.CUOTA)-2) ELSE '0' END AS CUOTA , CASE WHEN (B.CUOTA IS NOT NULL) THEN SUBSTR(B.CUOTA,-2,2) ELSE NULL END AS UNIDAD_CUOTA , B.CUOTA3 , B.TIME_PERIOD , DESARROLLO FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT TMCODE , CASE WHEN DESARROLLO = 'CONVERTIBLE' THEN TRANSLATE(VALOR_KB, ',','.') ELSE NULL END VALOR_KB FROM #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_SYSADM.CAP_CONF_DATOS WHERE TMCODE IS NOT NULL AND VALOR_KB IS NOT NULL) A INNER JOIN ( SELECT * FROM( SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY TMCODE ORDER BY CUOTA) NUM , TMCODE , SNCODE , CASE WHEN (CUOTA IS NOT NULL) THEN SUBSTR(CUOTA, INSTR(CUOTA,'_', 1, 1)+1, INSTR(CUOTA,'_',1,2)-INSTR(CUOTA,'_',1,1)-1) ELSE NULL END AS CUOTA , CASE WHEN (CUOTA3 IS NOT NULL) THEN SUBSTR(CUOTA3, INSTR(CUOTA3,'_', 1,1)+1, length(CUOTA3)) ELSE NULL END AS CUOTA3 , TIME_PERIOD , DESARROLLO FROM #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_SYSADM.CAP_CONF_DATOS WHERE (DESARROLLO NOT IN ('CONVERTIBLE')) AND TMCODE IS NOT NULL AND SNCODE IS NOT NULL) A WHERE NUM = 1) B ON A.TMCODE = B.TMCODE ) CAP INNER JOIN ( SELECT TMCODE , SNCODE , SPCODE , REC_VERSION FROM #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_SYSADM.MPULKTMB WHERE TMCODE IS NOT NULL AND SNCODE IS NOT NULL AND SPCODE IS NOT NULL AND VSCODE IN (SELECT MAX(REC_VERSION) FROM #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_SYSADM.MPULKTMB GROUP BY TMCODE,SPCODE,SNCODE)) MP ON CAP.TMCODE = MP.TMCODE AND CAP.SNCODE = MP.SNCODE) D FULL OUTER JOIN ( SELECT DISTINCT TMCODE , SPCODE_BASICO AS SPCODE , TIPO_OFERTA , PSB_CONVERTIBLE_LDI AS BAN_CONVERTIBLE_LDI , TO_CHAR(PSB_MINU_CONV_LDI) AS PSB_MINU_CONV_LDI , TO_CHAR(PSB_VALOR_CONV_LDI) AS PSB_VALOR_CONV_LDI , TO_CHAR(PSB_VALOR_CONV_PREFERE_LDI) AS PSB_VALOR_CONV_PREFERE_LDI , TO_CHAR(PSB_MINU_CONV_ZONA_LDI) AS PSB_MINU_CONV_ZONA_LDI , TO_CHAR(PSB_VALOR_CONV_ZONA_LDI) AS PSB_VALOR_CONV_ZONA_LDI , TO_CHAR(PSB_MINU_CONV_PREFERE_LDI) AS PSB_MINU_CONV_PREFERE_LDI FROM #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_SYSADM.INH_SOBRERENTAS WHERE TIPO_OFERTA = 'CONVERTIBLE' AND TMCODE IS NOT NULL AND SPCODE_BASICO IS NOT NULL ) V ON D.TMCODE = V.TMCODE AND D.SPCODE = V.SPCODE
SNP_PROJECT : CAPACITACION #SNP_FOLDER : DAVID #SNP_PACKAGE : ETL #SNP_SCEN : SC_JH_0772_CLIEN_CARGA_OBJETOS_NZLOAD Version 001
